when I reminisce about all those year of tribulation , I mostly remember our song . we die . and our blood seep away on the battlefield . but our song survive . together with those of us that return . and as they too will die one day , our song will live on and will be sing by our child and by our child 's child . this be how we will be remember . this be who we be : Helvetios . do aivi , do aivi ... ( forever , forever ... ) ______________ name epilogue Artist Eluveitie album Helvetios